name: Listened to Week 3 Hurry-Up: Sunglasses on

content.html:
Richard and Alex talk about a surprisingly wild third week of the college football season. Jay Norvell writes a check and doesn’t cash it against Colorado. Missouri and Kansas State play an absolute banger. WVU beats Pitt in the Backyard Brawl. Florida takes apart Tennessee. And much more in a 30(ish)-minute sprint through everything interesting that happened this weekend. Production: Anthony Vito.
